getRegion(int, int) - Method in class pkgGame.Sudoku
getRegion - figure out what region you're in based on iCol and iRow and call getRegion(int)
Example, the following Puzzle: 0 1 2 3
1 2 3 4
3 4 1 2
4 1 3 2
getRegion(0,3) would call getRegion(1) and return [2],[3],[3],[4]
getRegion(int) - Method in class pkgGame.Sudoku
getRegion - pass in a given region, get back a one-dimensional array of the region's content
Example, the following Puzzle: 0 1 2 3
1 2 3 4
3 4 1 2
4 1 3 2
getRegion(2) and return [3],[4],[4],[1]

getRegionNbr - Return region number based on given column and row Example, the following Puzzle: 0 1 2 3

4 1 3 2
